      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0002": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0002",
        "Text": "可以用<img id=\"Dash\"/>「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1405>」\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1405>中會消耗「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1504>」，而位於地面時能夠<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>\n只要<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1405>中<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1406>，\n就會發動比平常跳得更高的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1407>」"
