      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0014": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0014",
        "Text": "用<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1301>／<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>使<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>變成2"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0004": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0004",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0004": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0004",
        "Text": "以<img id=\"NormalAttack_1\"/>攻擊\n<img id=\"NormalAttack_2\"/>、<img id=\"NormalAttack_3\"/>也可以發動攻擊\n而且同時按下<img id=\"MoveDown\"/>可以發動別的攻擊"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0005": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0005",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1417>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0005": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0005",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>中會持續以敵方角色為目標\n發動攻擊就會自動以敵方為對象進行攻擊\n\n有複數敵人時可用<img id=\"TargetChangeLeft\"/><img id=\"TargetChangeRight\"/>切換攻擊對象"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0006": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0006",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0006": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0006",
        "Text": "用詛咒祓除詛咒的攻擊就是「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>」\n是對敵人造成傷害的基本手段\n\n<img id=\"CursedEnergyAttack_1\"/>和<img id=\"CursedEnergyAttack_2\"/>可以各使出不同的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>\n要使用這些招式，需要讓<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>量表累積<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>量表在使用過後會隨時間<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0007": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0007",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0007": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0007",
        "Text": "讓自己的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>上升的攻擊稱為「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>」\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>命中敵方會使<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>量表上升，到達一定的值就會讓自己的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>提升\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>升級的話，會強化<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>並增加傷害"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0015": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0015",
        "Text": "讓<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1301>成功"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0015": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0015",
        "Text": "<img id=\"NormalAttack_1\"/> 連續輸入"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0016": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0016",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1409>攻擊3次"
