      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0105": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0105",
        "Text": "<img id=\"Guard\"/>＋<img id=\"CursedEnergyAttack_2\"/>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0101": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0101",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1704>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0101": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0101",
        "Text": "可以用<img id=\"ChatUp\"/><img id=\"ChatDown\"/><img id=\"ChatLeft\"/><img id=\"ChatRight\"/>指示我方角色在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>時的行動\n\n<img id=\"Chat_0005\"/>一般：平均的行動\n<img id=\"Chat_0006\"/>猛攻：頻繁使用<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>\n<img id=\"Chat_0007\"/>協力：積極進行合作\n<img id=\"Chat_0008\"/>慎重：常用<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1431>和<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1409>，走位避免受傷"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0102",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1402>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0102",
        "Text": "和夥伴角色攻擊同一個敵人\n或是攻擊正在攻擊夥伴的敵人會產生「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1402>」\n出現獎勵後可以獲得追加的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1505>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0103": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0103",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1314>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0103": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0103",
        "Text": "用<img id=\"MoveDown\"/>＋<img id=\"NormalAttack_1\"/>可以使出「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1313>」\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1313>無法<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1409>，擊中敵方後，敵方就會變成特殊的受創狀態\n在敵方的受創狀態期間，夥伴的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1301>或<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>擊中敵方\n會發動和夥伴的合作攻擊「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1314>」\n\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1314>發動的話自己和夥伴的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>會上升\n並且可以對敵方造成大量傷害"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0104": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0104",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0104": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0104",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>最大時可以使用特殊招式「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>」\n同時輸入<img id=\"Guard\"/>和<img id=\"CursedEnergyAttack_2\"/>就可以發動\n招式效果有強力攻擊或<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>等，每個角色的招式效果不同\n另外<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>中只能發動一次"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0201",
        "Text": "讓<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>變成最大"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0202",
        "Text": "讓<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>成功"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0202",
        "Text": "<img id=\"Guard\"/>＋<img id=\"CursedEnergyAttack_2\"/>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0201",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0201",
        "Text": "一部分角色的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>可以發動<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>\n\n<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>成功的話，能將敵方和我方拉進自己的領域\n在領域內自己的能力會提升，對敵方造成妨礙效果和大傷害\n可以在有利的狀態展開<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0202",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0202",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>會因以下任一原因解除\n時間經過、發動者被<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1418>、有別的<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>覆蓋過原本的領域\n另外，也有從展開後攻擊，一連串進行到解除的類型存在\n\n一部分角色在<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>解除後的一定時間內\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>可能會受到限制，需要注意"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0301": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0301",
        "Text": "關於適應"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0301": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0301",
        "Text": "魔虛羅有「適應」對手攻擊，並使其無效的能力。\n擊敗魔虛羅的咒力技會被適應，之後無法造成損傷。\n招式如果被適應了，與招式對應的法陣圖示就會亮起。\n\n覺醒技可以造成損傷。\n最後就用這招式打敗魔虛羅吧。"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0001": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0001",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1001>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0001": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0001",
        "Text": "在「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1001>」可以體驗<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_0001>的故事\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>…\n　再次體驗<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0001>等人的戰鬥記錄\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>…\n　確認各角色的關係性"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0101",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0101",
        "Text": "在這裡可以照時間順序選擇任務體驗故事\n\n根據任務將有特殊的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1601>條件\n或「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1817>」這種課題的類型\n任務細節可按下<img id=\"PopupMenu_2\"/>確認"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0102",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>的進行"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0102",
        "Text": "推進<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>會讓<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>的角色開放\n以及角色之間的關係進展\n不時確認看看吧\n\n也可透過按下<img id=\"PopupMenu_1\"/>移動到<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0201",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0201",
        "Text": "在這裡可以確認角色之間的關係性\n進行<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>會讓角色之間的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1105>」上升\n可以獲得報酬，或是觀看開放的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1706>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0301": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0301",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1002>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_10",
        "Text": "在這裡可以連上網路進行線上對戰\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1102>…\n　可以輕鬆對戰\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1101>…\n　與實力相近的玩家們對戰"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_20",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1101>與實力相近的玩家們對戰\n依對戰結果和分數會讓「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1901>」變動\n也可以依累計分數獲得報酬\n詳情可在「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1208>」確認"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0401": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0401",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_10",
        "Text": "在這裡可以連上網路在線上和玩家協力\n以特殊規則進行與敵方的連續<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>…\n　可以和玩家協力\n　進行每次遊玩會變化，以「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1815>」構成的連續<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n　達成「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1817>」的條件並打倒敵人獲得高分吧\n　另外也有設有特殊勝敗條件的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_20",
        "Text": "・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1802>…\n　敵人比<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>更強的模式\n　請以完全攻略為目標"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0402": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0402",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0402": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0402",
        "Text": "先遊玩「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>」，體驗模式的流程吧\n第一次將是線下遊玩\n\n另外，第一次以後只要選擇「一個人遊玩」\n就可以在線下遊玩"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0403": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0403",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0403": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0403",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>只要遊玩「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>」就會變動\n當<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>上升，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>的難度\n和<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>的構成也會階段性變化\n協力的玩家將會優先配對<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>相近的玩家\n\n出擊時可以任意設定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>以調整難度\n※如果降低後出擊，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>上限不會提升"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0404": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0404",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>/<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0404": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0404",
        "Text": "另外，在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>\n可以「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>」特殊的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>道具」或角色而達到強化\n遊玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1802>以獲得<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1812>\n強化角色吧\n\n強化後會比較容易攻略困難的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0501": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0501",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0501": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0501",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>購買的道具的角色可以強化角色\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>最多可裝3個，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>角色就會開放欄位\n但是無法<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>複數個同一類型的道具\n\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>道具有可以永久<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>的類型\n和發揮一次效果就會消失的各種種類\n另外，遊玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>可能會讓<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>陳列新的道具"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0502": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0502",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0502": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0502",
        "Text": "可以使用遊玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1802>獲得的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1812>\n來提升角色的LV\nLV提升會強化數值，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>欄位會被開放\n\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1812>是遊玩任何角色都會共同累計，可以自由分配"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0601": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0601",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>的選擇"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0601": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0601",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>可以對自己設定「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>」\n設定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>將會限制行動或數值等，而強化其他能力\n\n在設定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>的狀態下通關任務，可以追加獲得<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>點數"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0701": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0701",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1831>可以做的事"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0701": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0701",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1831>畫面可以為了準備下個任務\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1422>」或個別的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1502>」\n各個<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>都需要點數\n點數是由玩家各自持有，好好運用<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>吧\n\n這個<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>點數可在任務通關時獲得\n另外，設定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>的狀態下通關任務，可以追加獲得點數"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0801": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0801",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1005>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0801": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0801",
        "Text": "在這裡可以自由設定角色和規則來遊玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n\n・角色設定…\n　可以設定我方和對手的角色選擇及強度\n\n・玩家設定…\n　可以設定特殊項目\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>設定…\n　可以設定關卡限制時間、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>等規則"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0901": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0901",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1004>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_10",
        "Text": "在這裡可以連接網路在線上建立大廳\n與<DYN=FRIEND_WORD>和陌生人等固定成員遊玩\n\n・建立大廳…以房主身分建立大廳\n　可以變更遊玩方式和招募文來募集風格契合的玩家\n\n・尋找大廳…參加已建立的大廳\n　搜尋<DYN=FRIEND_WORD>或ID可以直接參加特定大廳"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_20",
        "Text": "・角色選擇…\n　選擇在大廳操作的角色\n　在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>可以選擇別的角色，以喜歡的角色參加大廳吧！"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1001": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1001",
        "Text": "大廳房主可以做的事"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_10",
        "Text": "大廳房主長按<img id=\"BattlePause\"/>開始<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n成員到齊以後就開始吧"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_20",
        "Text": "另外，可以用<img id=\"BattlePause\"/>打開選單做以下動作\n\n・出擊模式的設定…\n　可以變更大廳成員遊玩的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>模式\n\n・玩家的踢除…\n　可以從大廳踢除玩家\n　這項操作要從大廳情報進行"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1002": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1002",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1004>可以做的事"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_10",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1004>可以做以下動作\n\n・定型<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>…\n　用<img id=\"ChatUp\"/><img id=\"ChatDown\"/><img id=\"ChatLeft\"/><img id=\"ChatRight\"/>進行定型<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>\n\n・不顯示UI…\n　可用<img id=\"WidgetDispSwitch\"/>切換UI的顯示／不顯示"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_20",
        "Text": "・切換視角模式…\n　可以切換成能用<img id=\"CameraUp\"/><img id=\"CameraDown\"/><img id=\"CameraLeft\"/><img id=\"CameraRight\"/>自由移動視角的模式\n\n大廳房主開始<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n而要退出大廳可用<img id=\"BattlePause\"/>顯示選單"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1101",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1101",
        "Text": "在這裡可以使用從<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>等獲得的<img id=\"Money_0001\"/><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2103>\n購買<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2217>或<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1207>的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>道具\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>專用道具等\n\n一部分道具為達成條件後可以購買"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1102",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2102>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1102",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2102>是可以<GLO=GLS_NAME_MAP_00>獲得<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>道具的道具\n\n※不包含有開放條件的道具\n※如果抽中已取得，或是數量超過上限數量的道具\n將轉變為<img id=\"Money_0001\"/><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2103>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1201": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1201",
        "Text": "關於<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1201": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1201",
        "Text": "可以在這裡觀察角色\n進行各種<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1202": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1202",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1207><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1202": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1202",
        "Text": "可以照喜好<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1207>\n\n個別的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>道具可透過遊玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>或是在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>購買來獲得"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1203": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1203",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1203": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1203",
        "Text": "可以照喜好<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>中的定型<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>\n\n不同角色可以個別設定\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>適合遊玩風格的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>吧"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1204": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1204",
        "Text": "VS姿勢／<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>語音<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1204": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1204",
